      {
        "lines": [
          {
            "role": "旁白",
            "english": "Last night, Wang Peng and Li You went to Gao Wenzhong's house to hang out. At Gao Wenzhong's house, they met Gao Wenzhong's older sister. Her name is Gao Xiaoyin, and she works at the school library. She invited Wang Peng to drink tea, and Wang Peng drank two cups. Li You doesn't drink tea, she only drank a cup of water. They chatted and watched TV together. Wang Peng and Li You didn't go home until twelve o'clock at night.",
